text: August H. Dean (born August 19, 1994) is an American professional stock car racing driver. He last competed part-time in the NASCAR Xfinity Series driving the No. 15 Ford Mustang for AM Racing and in the ARCA Menards Series, driving the No. 55 Toyota Camry for Venturini Motorsports. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1994 births Category:NASCAR drivers Category:Sportspeople from South Carolina
